In the Matter of the Application of James F. Egan, as Public Administrator of the County of New York, Respondent, for Revocation of Letters of Administration Issued to Gunda K. Morland on the Estate of Hans Morland, Deceased. Gunda K. Morland, as Temporary Administratrix of the Estate of Hans Morland, Deceased, Appellant; Klara Morland et al., Respondents.

Decree unanimously affirmed, with costs.

No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Untermyer and Dore, JJ. [184 Misc. 435, 439.] [See post, p. 745.]
